quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,"Observe/guard on the prayers, and the prayers the middle, and stand/call to God obeying/worshipping humbly"
  2,239,"So if you feared, so walking or riding , so if you became safe/secure , so mention/remember God, as He taught you what you were not knowing"
  2,240,"And those who are made to die from you, and they leave spouses/wives , a bequest to their spouses/wives, alimony/enjoyment to the year without/not bringing out/forcing out, so if they (F) got out , so no offense/guilt/sin on you, in what they made/did in themselves (F) from kindness/known/goodness, and God (is) glorious/mighty , wise/judicious"
  2,241,And for the divorcees (F) alimony with the kindness/generosity deservedly/rightfully on the fearing and obeying (God)
  2,242,"Like that God clarifies to you His verses/evidences , maybe you reason/understand/ comprehend"
  2,243,"Do you not see/understand to those who got out from their homes/countries/tribes/places , and they are thousands , fearing/cautioning the death, so God said to them: \"Die.\" Then He revived them. That God (is owner) of grace/favour/blessing on the people, and but most of the people do not thank/be grateful"
  2,244,"And fight/kill in God`s way/road/sake, and know that God (is) hearing/listening, knowledgeable"
  2,245,"Who (is) that who lends/advances God a good loan/advance, so He (God) doubles/multiplies it for him many doubles/multiples, and God holds/tightens and spreads/widens , and to Him you are being returned"